/-- Recursive full-stage facts imply recursive source-closure data.

This threads the one-column and two-step full-stage constructors through the
same two-step induction used by the source-closure conversion.  The remaining
stored-loop task is now isolated to proving
`storedSignedSequenceTwiceTrailingFullStageSourceClosureData` from the actual
per-pivot loop hypotheses. -/
